nd layer over cheese filling. Tuck edges of filo down around sides of dish, then score top layer of pie with a sharp knife into 8 equal-sized portions, sprinkle with water and garnish with sesame seeds (if using)."},{"content":"Bake for 25-30 minutes (200°C) until golden brown. Leave to cool for 5 minutes before serving warm or at room temperature."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Add <b>2 tsp<b> dried mint in <b>step 4<b> for a different flavour.","Cover filo pastry sheets with a damp tea towel to prevent them drying out as you work.","Serve tiropita with a green salad."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","1h 10m","8 portions"]}